uot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://gradle.org/&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Gradle&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have noticed a rise in recruiting impersonations across the industry, where scammers attempt to access candidates&#39; personal and financial information through fake interviews and offers. All Fingerprint recruiting email communications will always come from the @fingerprint.com domain. Any outreach claiming to be from Fingerprint via other sources should be ignored.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre looking for a strategic and collaborative&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing Demand Generation team. In this role, you‚Äôll own and scale our 1:few ABM programs and drive coordinated multi-channel campaigns in partnership with our BDR, content, and product marketing teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to help evolve Fingerprint‚Äôs go-to-market strategy, bringing creativity and precision to how we engage enterprise accounts across the buyer journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, launch, and manage &lt;strong&gt;multi-channel ABM campaigns&lt;/strong&gt; across paid media, direct mail, email, and BDR outreach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the BDR team on &lt;strong&gt;account-triggered outreach&lt;/strong&gt; strategies, ensuring alignment on messaging and timing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product marketing and content to develop tailored content for key personas and industries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale and optimize our &lt;strong&gt;1:few ABM strategy&lt;/strong&gt; across high-priority segments and use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage &lt;strong&gt;experimentation programs&lt;/strong&gt; to drive engagement, qualified pipeline, and conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead &lt;strong&gt;persona segmentation&lt;/strong&gt; and journey mapping to refine outreach and content personalization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee &lt;strong&gt;ABM landing pages&lt;/strong&gt;, driving continuous optimization for conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and report on &lt;strong&gt;ABM success metrics&lt;/strong&gt;, sharing insights through dashboards and monthly write-ups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support targeted &lt;strong&gt;1:1 ABM efforts&lt;/strong&gt; and collaborate cross-functionally with growth and design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explore and implement &lt;strong&gt;product-qualified ABM&lt;/strong&gt; strategies to align with our product-led growth motion&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We‚Äôre Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years in &lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation or ABM&lt;/strong&gt;, ideally in a &lt;strong&gt;SaaS&lt;/strong&gt; or high-growth tech environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience executing &lt;strong&gt;enterprise-scale ABM campaigns&lt;/strong&gt; using platforms like LinkedIn, Meta (Facebook/Instagram), and direct mail tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong &lt;strong&gt;collaboration skills&lt;/strong&gt; with BDR or sales teams to align on outreach strategies and optimize performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with &lt;strong&gt;A/B testing&lt;/strong&gt;, data analysis, and &lt;strong&gt;conversion rate optimization&lt;/strong&gt; (CRO)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of &lt;strong&gt;buyer journeys&lt;/strong&gt;, persona development, and segmentation tactics&lt;/li&gt;
