&lt;p&gt;By becoming a part of the Fingerprint talent community, you&#39;ll gain several advantages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Firstly, you&#39;ll be among the first to know about any future job openings that match your qualifications and aspirations. This means you&#39;ll have a head start in applying for positions that interest you, maximizing your chances of landing your dream job.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additionally, joining our talent community provides an opportunity for those with referrals to submit them, even if we don&#39;t have a suitable position open at the moment. We appreciate the power of connections and understand that great talent often comes through recommendations. Your referrals can help us discover hidden gems and extraordinary individuals who may be a perfect fit for our team in the future&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When you join our talent community, you&#39;ll receive regular updates on Fingerprint news, events, and industry insights. You&#39;ll also have access to exclusive content and resources that can enhance your professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We encourage you to submit your application to join Fingerprint&#39;s talent community by clicking the &quot;Apply Now&quot; button below. Please include your updated resume or CV, along with any additional information that highlights your skills, achievements, and career interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We appreciate your interest in our organization and look forward to getting to know you better. Your decision to join our talent community opens doors to future possibilities and ensures that you&#39;re on our radar when new opportunities arise. Please note that submitting your application to Fingerprint&#39;s talent community is not equivalent to applying for a specific open position. Instead, it allows us to stay connected, nurture our relationship, and explore potential avenues for collaboration in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thank you for considering joining our talent community. We appreciate your time and effort, and we are excited to embark on this journey together.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have noticed a rise in recruiting impersonations across the industry, where scammers attempt to access candidates&#39; personal and financial information through fake interviews and offers. All Fingerprint recruiting email communications will always come from the @fingerprint.com domain. Any outreach claiming to be from Fingerprint via other sources should be ignored.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Offers vary depending on, but not limited to, relevant experience, education, certifications/licenses, skills, training, and market conditions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to regulatory and security reasons, there‚Äôs a small number of countries where we cannot have Fingerprint teammates based.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Additionally, because Fingerprint is an all-remote company and people can join our workforce from almost any country, we do not sponsor visas. Fingerprint teammates need to be authorized to work from their home location&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are dedicated to creating an inclusive work environment for everyone. We embrace and celebrate the unique experiences, perspectives and cultural backgrounds that each employee brings to our workplace. Fingerprint strives to foster an environment where our employees feel respected, valued and empowered, and our team members are at the forefront in helping us promote and sustain an inclusive workplace. We highly encourage people from underrepresented groups in tech to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are applying as a resident of California, please read our CCPA notice &lt;a href=&quot;https://dev.fingerprint.com/docs/dpa-ccpa&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are applying as a resident of the EU, please read our GDPR notice &lt;a href=&quot;https://dev.fingerprint.com/docs/dpa-gdpr&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fingerprint&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;empowers developers to stop online fraud at the source.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work on turning radical new ideas in the fraud detection space into reality. Our products are developer-focused and our clients range from solo developers to publicly traded companies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;We are a globally dispersed, 100% remote company&lt;/strong&gt; with a strong open-source focus. Our flagship open-source project is &lt;a class=&quot;c-link c-link--focus-visible&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/fingerprintjs/fingerprintjs&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://github.com/fingerprintjs/fingerprintjs&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;FingerprintJS&lt;/a&gt; (20K stars on GitHub).&lt;/p&gt;
