&lt;p&gt;#LI-remote&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 900;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere, impact everywhere&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity is at the heart of who we are at Xapo Bank. We‚Äôre a fully distributed team of over 140 Xapiens that work remotely from 40+ countries around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our beginning: A world that enjoys economic freedom and wealth protection, no matter where you live or who is running your country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To achieve that, we search the world for the best people for the job. We work hard, think globally, and inspire each other to learn and grow. We are committed to changing the way things are done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk is inherent in all of our business activities and managing risk well is the responsibility of every Xapien. Sound risk management enables us to serve our customers and deliver value for our shareholders, and helps make Xapo a great place to work.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Although we are headquartered in Gibraltar, this is a full time, 100% remote position&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Position overview&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Legal Analyst you will be responsible for supporting our legal team particularly in the areas of conducting research, reviewing documentation, contracts, engagement terms, analysing complex legal information and summarising findings in clear, concise reports.&amp;nbsp; This role is instrumental in allowing the Legal team and Xapo to make informed decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct in-depth legal research on a wide range of legal topics and areas of law.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review legal documentation and information relevant to the Financial Services, Fintech, and Blockchain spaces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assessing and implementing standards relating to the consumer duty principle, financial promotion rules, and reviewing and assessing client facing communications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dealing with any issues that arise from a members‚Äô perspective.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyse this information and provide concise reports based on findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide recommendations and sound legal advice based on research findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Skills needed&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: solid PQE within the Financial Services (primarily banking, payments and DLT) industry, with a Fintech and Blockchain focus ideally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualification: UK qualified lawyer or equivalent but with practice and experience in the UK or Gibraltar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skills: Demonstrated analytical and research abilities. The capacity to analyse complex legal issues and conduct thorough legal research is crucial. This involves sifting through large amounts of information, and distilling it into something manageable and understandable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem-Solving Skills: Ability to find creative solutions to complex legal problems. This requires innovative thinking and a proactive approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail: A high level of accuracy and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technological Proficiency: Our work involves various technologies and infrastructure. Familiarity with these tools and ability to interact with a global team digitally is important.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project Management: Ability to lead a project, interact across product, risk, finance and other teams within the group, and to have some business development skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Other requirements&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated workspace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A reliable internet connection with the fastest speed possible in your area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devices and other essential equipment that meet minimal technical specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alignment with Our Values and the Xapo Values-Driven Leadership principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why work for Xapo?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;IMPACT GLOBALLY, WORK REMOTELY.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape the Future:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; Improve lives through cutting-edge technology, work 100% remotely from anywhere in the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great work-life balance:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Build amazing things with a balance of autonomy and collaborative teamwork. Set your own work schedule and make use of a flexible PTO plan when you need to recharge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expect Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; Collaborate, learn, and grow with a high-performance team. Learn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; how you learn best - from books to conferences, you‚Äôll get a yearly budget for your individual learning and development goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Xapo, we prioritize consumer protection and adhere to regulatory requirements by ensuring that all Xapiens are accountable for upholding principles of fair treatment, transparency, and ethical conduct in their interactions with customers and stakeholders.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Xapo Device Policy&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Consultants joining Xapo Bank must comply with the Xapo Device Policy, which governs the use of corporate-approved laptops under Corporate-Owned, Personally Purchased Device (reimbursed up to $1,500) or Corporate-Owned, Personally Enabled Device (personal device with enforced security controls).&lt;br&gt;All devices must meet security requirements, enroll in Xapo‚Äôs Mobile Device Management (MDM), and adhere to compliance rules. COPPD devices remain Xapo property with buyback options upon exit. COPED users agree to data control measures, including mandatory corporate data wipes.&lt;br&gt;Compliance with the Xapo Device Policy is mandatory for all consultants, onboarding will not proceed without adherence to the policy.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 900;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere, impact everywhere&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity is at the heart of who we are at Xapo Bank. We‚Äôre a fully distributed team of over 140 Xapiens that work remotely from 40+ countries around the world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our beginning: A world that enjoys economic freedom and wealth protection, no matter where you live or who is running your country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To achieve that, we search the world for the best people for the job. We work hard, think globally, and inspire each other to learn and grow. We are committed to changing the way things are done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk is inherent in all of our business activities and managing risk well is the responsibility of every Xapien. Sound risk management enables us to serve our customers and deliver value for our shareholders, and helps make Xapo a great place to work.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Although we are headquartered in Gibraltar, this is a full time, 100% remote position&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Work from anywhere!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Legal Counsel at Xapo, you‚Äôll be a core legal partner to our banking and fund activities, with a particular focus on the governance, structuring, and legal oversight of the &lt;strong&gt;Xapo Fund&lt;/strong&gt;.You will be responsible for ensuring robust compliance and governance while leveraging strong expertise in financial market structures and derivatives to support our broader investment strategy. Reporting to the Chief Legal Officer, you will lead legal negotiations, ensure robust fund compliance, and partner closely with our external fund manager to support and evaluate structured product transactions, derivatives-based opportunities, and other complex financial instruments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to work at the intersection of banking, crypto, and investment management‚Äîadvising on cutting-edge financial products while ensuring world-class legal and regulatory standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Transaction Structuring &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead negotiation and execution of legal agreements for fund investments, including structured finance transactions, derivatives, lending agreements&amp;nbsp; and other strategic opportunities aligned with the Xapo Fund‚Äôs strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support legal assessment of new fund investment opportunities, particularly those involving complex financial instruments, ensuring compliance with relevant banking, investment and derivatives regulations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;External Manager Oversight (Legal Interface)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the legal point of contact between Xapo and the Xapo Fund‚Äôs external investment manager, Hilbert Capital, ensuring legal integrity in our partnership and communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the smooth operation and evolution of the Xapo Fund‚Äôs legal architecture in collaboration with internal and external stakeholders, with a keen focus on best practices in traditional financial market operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fund Governance &amp;amp; Control&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, draft, and advise on key fund documentation, including constitutional documents, offering memoranda, investment management agreements, and investor contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure fund structures and operations remain aligned with legal, regulatory, and governance expectations, including derivatives-related disclosures and compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Member Offering &amp;amp; Disclosures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Compliance teams to ensure clarity, accuracy, and compliance in customer-facing fund materials (e.g. investor updates, risk disclosures, marketing collateral, terms &amp;amp; conditions), especially when pertaining to structured and derivative product offerings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Broader Legal Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide commercial legal advice across Xapo‚Äôs fintech and banking operations, particularly in areas of traditional financial regulation, derivatives, payments, crypto, and digital assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support general legal operations including vendor contracts, commercial negotiations, and cross-functional initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor evolving regulatory landscapes (especially Gibraltar, United Kingdom and European frameworks) to ensure Xapo‚Äôs products remain compliant and future-fit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Skills needed:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 5+ years PQE as a qualified lawyer, with strong experience in financial services, investment funds, fintech or crypto. Exposure to traditional banking, financial market structuring, and derivatives transactions is highly desirable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualification:&lt;/strong&gt; UK qualified solicitor or equivalent with experience in the United Kingdom, Gibraltar or Europe. Previous in-house counsel experience preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Solid understanding of investment fund documentation, investment regulations, derivatives documentation and DLT frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Excellent research, drafting, and contract negotiation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Able to navigate fast-paced environments and partner across legal, risk, product, and external firms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attention to Detail:&lt;/strong&gt; High level of precision, particularly when it comes to member-facing materials and regulatory compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Autonomy &amp;amp; Initiative:&lt;/strong&gt; Comfortable working independently on high-impact projects with a solutions-oriented mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Other requirements:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated workspace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A reliable internet connection with the fastest speed possible in your area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devices and other essential equipment that meet minimal technical specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alignment with Our Values and the Xapo Values-Driven Leadership principles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why work for Xapo?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;IMPACT GLOBALLY, WORK REMOTELY.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape the Future:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; Improve lives through cutting-edge technology, work 100% remotely from anywhere in the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Great work-life balance:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;Build amazing things with a balance of autonomy and collaborative teamwork. Set your own work schedule and make use of a flexible PTO plan when you need to recharge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expect Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; Collaborate, learn, and grow with a high-performance team. Learn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 500;&quot;&gt; how you learn best - from books to conferences, you‚Äôll get a yearly budget for your individual learning and development goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Xapo, we prioritize consumer protection and adhere to regulatory requirements by ensuring that all Xapiens are accountable for upholding principles of fair treatment, transparency, and ethical conduct in their interactions with customers and stakeholders.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Xapo Device Policy&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Consultants joining Xapo Bank must comply with the Xapo Device Policy, which governs the use of corporate-approved laptops under Corporate-Owned, Personally Purchased Device (reimbursed up to $1,500) or Corporate-Owned, Personally Enabled Device (personal device with enforced security controls).&lt;br&gt;All devices must meet security requirements, enroll in Xapo‚Äôs Mobile Device Management (MDM), and adhere to compliance rules. COPPD devices remain Xapo property with buyback options upon exit. COPED users agree to data control measures, including mandatory corporate data wipes.&lt;br&gt;Compliance with the Xapo Device Policy is mandatory for all consultants, onboarding will not proceed without adherence to the policy.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;c-message_kit__blocks c-message_kit__blocks--rich_text&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;c-message__message_blocks c-message__message_blocks--rich_text&quot; data-qa=&quot;message-text&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-block_kit_renderer&quot; data-qa=&quot;block-kit-renderer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-block_kit_renderer__block_wrapper p-block_kit_renderer__block_wrapper--first&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_block&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alpaca is a US California headquartered brokerage infrastructure technology company and self-clearing broker-dealer, delivering execution and custody solutions for Stocks, ETFs, Options, Cryptocurrencies, and more, and has raised over $170 million in funding. Amongst our subsidiaries, Alpaca is a licensed financial services company in multiple countries, and we serve hundreds of financial institutions globally such as broker-dealers, investment advisors, hedge funds, and crypto exchanges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alpaca‚Äôs globally distributed team members bring in diverse experiences such as engineers, traders, and brokerage professionals to achieve our Mission of opening financial services to everyone on the planet. We are also deeply committed to open-source contributions and fostering a vibrant community. We will continue to enhance and improve our award-winning developer-friendly API and the infrastructure behind it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Team Members:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre a team of 150+ globally distributed members who love working from our favorite places worldwide. Our team spans the USA, Canada, Japan, Hungary, Nigeria, Brazil, the United Kingdom, and more!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre looking for candidates eager to join Alpaca‚Äôs growing organization, who are excited about our Mission of ‚ÄúOpen financial services to everyone on the planet and share our Values of ‚ÄúStay Curious,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave Empathy,‚Äù and ‚ÄúBe Accountable.‚Äù&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our brokerage product team at Alpaca is looking for a Lead Product Manager to define and drive new product initiatives and manage a portfolio of existing products. In this role you will ideate and deliver brokerage features while closely collaborating with engineering, analytics, design, partnerships and many other cross-functional teams across Alpaca.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Things You Get To Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own brokerage products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write product requirements and work with engineers to execute programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive brokerage product strategy by analyzing ROI, market competition, and build-vs-buy scenarios&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve the brokerage operation efficiency by providing solutions and owning the metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the product roadmap and product strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead customer calls around brokerage process and product issues to gain insights and reduce&amp;nbsp;them to products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in calls with external regulators to drive the product strategy and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report timely and accurately on product status and results to internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ad hoc duties and projects as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are (Must-Haves):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excited about what Alpaca is building&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in computer science or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in Product Management, Engineering, and/or starting a startup&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated interest in Brokerage and FinTech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience analyzing data using SQL and a relevant BI tool&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills, both written and verbal and collaboration skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business acumen to understand tradeoffs between stakeholders and technology feasibility with time and budget constraints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Might Be&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;strong&gt;Nice-to-Haves):&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience and background working on and developing Brokerage products is a plus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical background working with APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How We Take Care of You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Competitive Salary &amp;amp; Stock Options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Benefits: Health benefits start on day 1. In the US this includes Medical, Dental, Vision. In Canada, this includes supplemental health care. In Japan, you are offered local benefits. Internationally, this includes a stipend value to offset medical costs.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;New Hire Home-Office Setup: One-time USD $500&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Monthly Stipend: USD $150 per month via a Brex Card&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work with awesome hard working people, super smart and cool clients and innovative partners from around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Alpaca is proud to be an equal opportunity workplace dedicated to pursuing and hiring a diverse workforce.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://files.alpaca.markets/disclosures/AlpacaRecruitmentPrivacyPolicy.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recruitment Privacy Policy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At OneLocal, we provide SaaS solutions that help small and medium businesses (SMBs) grow through data-driven marketing strategies. Our 10 digital marketing solutions work seamlessly together, empowering businesses to navigate the ever-evolving marketing landscape.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a customer-facing&lt;strong&gt; Marketing Strategist&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;who thrives in a fast-paced environment and is eager to make an impact. If you&#39;re passionate about strategic marketing, client success, and digital growth, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You‚Äôll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult &amp;amp; Advise: Meet with clients to assess marketing needs, answer questions, and provide strategic guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set Expectations &amp;amp; Communicate Value: Clearly explain marketing strategies, performance expectations, and ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop &amp;amp; Optimize Campaigns: Craft marketing plans tailored to client goals, ensuring alignment with branding and industry trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze &amp;amp; Report: Use GA4, Google Search Console, and other analytics tools to track performance and provide actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate &amp;amp; Innovate: Work closely with Account Managers and our Agency team to enhance client marketing strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive Growth: Identify expansion opportunities to maximize value for clients and contribute to OneLocal‚Äôs success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years in a customer-facing marketing role (SaaS, marketing agency, or tech startup preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SEO expertise: Keyword research, technical SEO, content marketing, listings management, and Google Business Profile optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong digital marketing knowledge, including content marketing, inbound strategies, and paid advertising (Google &amp;amp; Facebook).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with website platforms (Duda, WordPress, Shopify) and CRM systems (Salesforce preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication &amp;amp; client management skills - you can build strong relationships and simplify complex strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage multiple clients in a dynamic, fast-moving environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management skills, including experience with tools like Jira.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You‚Äôll Love Working Here:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to have a major impact at a growing company that is helping small and medium sized businesses grow their digital presence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remote first: We have committed to a remote-first/distributed team work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid vacation + paid personal days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At OneLocal, we are committed to building and fostering an environment where our employees feel included, valued, and heard. Our belief is that a strong commitment to diversity and inclusion enables us to truly create the best company culture possible. We strongly encourage applications from candidates of all backgrounds, experience, and perspectives regardless of race, gender, sexual orientation, marital status, age, citizenship, disability, and national origin.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission at Sourcegraph is to make it so that &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.notion.so/sourcegraph/Mission-values-e9d37e6b972a4ef395c3076aea2bd07d?pvs=4&quot;&gt;everyone can code&lt;/a&gt;, not just ~0.1% of the population.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are transforming how the world‚Äôs most important companies build software by industrializing development with AI. Today, most professional developers spend a disproportionate amount of time understanding code and performing repetitive, low-level tasks‚Äîleaving less time for innovation and meaningful impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre changing that. Sourcegraph brings AI-powered search and agents to the enterprise, helping teams automate the mundane and amplify what developers do best‚Äî solving hard problems and creating great products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here‚Äôs how we‚Äôre making a difference:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accelerating developers &lt;/strong&gt;with AI agents that deliver insights and precision‚Äîenabling 5x faster test creation, 30% increase in merge requests, and saving 20 minutes per developer daily.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automating repetitive tasks,&lt;/strong&gt; from remediating vulnerabilities (saving teams 1,000+ hours annually) to speeding up migrations that would take years to months.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enabling innovation&lt;/strong&gt; by addressing complex problems like automated bug triage, vulnerability detection, and AI-driven code reviews seamlessly integrated into workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trusted by 7/10 top software companies by market cap, 4/6 top US banks and many of the companies leading global innovation, like Stripe, Indeed, Tesla, and 1Password, and with $225M in funding from investors like &lt;a href=&quot;https://techcrunch.com/2021/07/13/sourcegraph-raises-125m-series-d-on-2-6b-valuation-for-universal-code-search-tool/&quot;&gt;a16z&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://about.sourcegraph.com/blog/series-c-with-sequoia/&quot;&gt;Sequoia&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.redpoint.com/companies/sourcegraph/&quot;&gt;Redpoint&lt;/a&gt;, we are building the tools that will define the next era of enterprise software development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you‚Äôre passionate about solving the hardest problems in software and shaping the future of technology, join us. Let‚Äôs build something extraordinary together.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours &amp;amp; location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üåé While we hire &lt;a href=&quot;https://sourcegraph.notion.site/How-we-engage-talent-outside-of-the-US-218f7193695a46cbb1ef39ef9c1f72d4&quot;&gt;almost anywhere&lt;/a&gt; in the world, we expect those living in a hub city (Denver, Austin, or San Francisco) to be able to work from one of our office locations for several days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideal locations:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;San Francisco, CA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Denver, CO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Austin, TX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We do not subscribe to ‚ÄúI do my best work when I work 40 hours a week.‚Äù &amp;nbsp;People we hire at Sourcegraph believe that building outstanding things means working very hard ‚Äî smarter and more hours than the competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why this job is exciting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Solutions Engineer, you will have broad responsibility and growth potential in helping us take our pre-sales organization to the next level. Our customers are the world&#39;s leading technology organizations. No other role at any other company gives you insight into how so many world-class organizations and developers build software at scale, and no other role at any other company puts you right in the middle of it all like we do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìÖ Within one month, you will‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn about our products, our value propositions, our customers, our team, and our processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up your own fully configured sandbox instance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start building a trusting relationship with your peers on Sales, Value Engineering, Post-sales Customer Success and Support teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join customer and prospect calls with some of our largest customers to understand their needs, how we communicate the value of Sourcegraph, and how we deliver positive impact to our customers‚Äô business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get demo certified&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìÖ Within three months, you will‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continue to take ownership of more prospective relationships partnering with up to three Account Executives (AEs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead early-stage conversations with prospective customers and delve into the technical needs for success&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an advocate on behalf of your customers by bringing important insights and feedback back to internal teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drawing from past experience, as well as observations, make internal contributions by identifying opportunities to help propose and deliver solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Solutions Engineer-led projects which will mature our own capabilities, increase the breadth of our footprint both internally and externally, and positively impact our business and our customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìÖ Within six months, you will‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish yourself as a thought leader and evangelist by using your insights to teach prospective customers new and better ways to get value from Sourcegraph.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor, recruit and train teammates, prospects, and new hires&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are an enthusiastic, proactive, driven, and results-oriented Solutions Engineer who shares&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.sourcegraph.com/company/values&quot;&gt; our values&lt;/a&gt; and has a passion for getting prospective customers to that a-ha moment with Sourcegraph!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have at least 2 years experience in a relevant role such as pre-Sales Engineering or Solutions Engineering across a technical product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience selling Enterprise software solutions and have gone through the lived experience of the Enterprise process selling motions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have an innate curiosity of getting to the root of customer problems and understanding their motivations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You‚Äôre excited about the prospect of being directly involved in the advent of generative AI!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are well versed in back end infrastructure architecture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are very technically inclined and have a propensity to code and or hack code.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience writing code in one of the following (JavaScript, Python, Java, Go).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a problem solver, love to troubleshoot.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience troubleshooting Docker and Kubernetes environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills, specifically across technical presentations and product demonstrations; ability to influence and excite a technical audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Either through direct experience or deep understanding, working knowledge of the end-to-end software development lifecycle and concepts such as continuous integration and continuous deployment. Note: You do not need to be a software engineer to be successful in this role!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have the ability to speak fluently with our developer champions and users (who are all developers themselves).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have the strategic mindset to be able to identify opportunities and potential solutions to solve both internal and external problems or gaps, and you can use your skills to apply the appropriate solution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy building tools, templates, and technical enablement collateral.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have an organized approach to work, with demonstrated ability to proactively manage a set of concurrent opportunities, to make difficult prioritization decisions, and to use data to guide decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You‚Äôre not afraid to learn a new skill to solve a problem that benefits or unblocks a deal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You work well independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Level&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìä This job is an IC2 or IC3 position, depending on previous experience and role scope.&amp;nbsp; You can read more about &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.notion.so/sourcegraph/Leveling-Guide-0e1b5c76ada64b9caac387f8b7c4fc66&quot;&gt;our job leveling philosophy&lt;/a&gt; in our Handbook.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üí∏ We pay you an above-average salary&lt;/strong&gt; because we want to hire the best people who are fully focused on helping Sourcegraph succeed, not worried about paying bills. As an &lt;a href=&quot;https://sourcegraph.notion.site/Mission-values-e9d37e6b972a4ef395c3076aea2bd07d&quot;&gt;open and transparent&lt;/a&gt; company that values &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.notion.so/sourcegraph/Compensation-Pay-Transparency-at-Sourcegraph-d58d0774f51b4b489d41c3628d30ff8d?pvs=4&quot;&gt;competitive compensation&lt;/a&gt;, our compensation ranges are visible to every single Sourcegraph teammate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your salary is determined by your pay band for the IC2 - IC3 job level. For determining pay bands, we use a number of market and data-driven salary sources, along with your location zone, and target the high-end of the range to ensure we‚Äôre always paying above market regardless of where you live in the world. Both U.S. and international locations are divided into one of four zones, determined by the cost of labor index for each area. The salary for a successful candidate will be based on level, job-related skills, experience, qualifications, and location zone. Please note that the salaries below may be adjusted in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üí∞ The target compensation for this role is based on the IC2 - IC3 pay band for your zone. The IC2 -IC3 pay bands for each zone are listed below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IC2: $123,000 base + $41,000 variable ($164,000 USD on-target-earnings)&lt;br&gt;IC3: $150,000 base + $50,000 variable ($200,000 USD on-target-earnings)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please speak with a recruiter for additional information regarding zone locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìà In addition to our cash compensation, we offer equity (because when we succeed as a company, we want you to succeed, too) and generous &lt;a href=&quot;https://sourcegraph.notion.site/Benefits-Perks-dd1da4b6b3a64780abed010a144d34ba&quot;&gt;perks &amp;amp; benefits&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(243, 78, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Below is the interview process you can expect for this role (you can read more about &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://sourcegraph.notion.site/Types-of-interviews-f279f080583d49ee9f2c60e30c8cb1f7&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;the types of interviews&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; in our Handbook). It may look like a lot of steps, but rest assured that we move quickly and the steps are designed to help you get the information needed to determine if we‚Äôre the right fit for you‚Ä¶ Interviewing is a two-way street, after all!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We expect the interview process to take 3.25 hours in total.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;üëã Introduction Stage&lt;/strong&gt; - we have initial conversations to get to know you better‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
