&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In addition to defining the infrastructure as code, you will improve Canonical products and the open-source technologies they‚Äôre based on by providing critical feedback to developers on how their products operate at scale. This is done by submitting bugs (and sometimes writing pull requests) and collaborating on design and implementations with other teams within the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You‚Äôll be part of a global team of SREs that work together and support each other to provide the best possible services to our company, Canonical‚Äôs customers and the Ubuntu Community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
