&lt;li&gt;Sync with Marketing and Sales Leadership on GTM strategy and plans to achieve quarterly goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet with cross-functional teams to learn about our customers and use cases, and watch recorded sales calls to learn about our product and how we position it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Immediately own and execute on pipeline development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dig into the data and assess channel and campaign performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and socialize your 30-60-90 plan, including pipeline strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;üìÖ Within two months, you will‚Ä¶&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
