&lt;li&gt;Partner with the sales and business operations teams on attribution tracking, funnel reporting &amp;amp; analytics dashboards to give company-wide visibility into all GTM efforts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete a lead-scoring audit and implement any recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearly define demand generation priorities, goals, and strategy and build a framework for data-driven experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start to execute against your plan, capitalizing on the biggest opportunities for optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forecast, track, analyze, and report on the impact of demand activities on pipeline, revenue, and funnel velocity&lt;/li&gt;
