&lt;h3&gt;About Canonical&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canonical is a pioneering tech firm at the forefront of the global move to open source. As the company that publishes Ubuntu, one of the most important open source projects and the platform for AI, IoT and the cloud, we are changing the world of software. We recruit on a global basis and set a very high standard for people joining the company. We expect excellence - in order to succeed, we need to be the best at what we do. Most colleagues at Canonical have worked from home since its inception in 2004.‚Äã Working here is a step into the future, and will challenge you to think differently, work smarter, learn new skills, and raise your game.&lt;/p&gt;
