&lt;p&gt;Our ambition is to set a standard of excellence when it comes to serving the open source ecosystem. This is your chance to be a part of that as a &lt;strong&gt;Community Engineer at Canonical&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building community management at scale. We have multiple positions available, at different seniority levels.&lt;/p&gt;
